              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>The frontmatter of a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/index.xml" title="Forester" addr="forest://forester/index" type="local">Forester</fr:link> <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="forest://forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">tree</fr:link> is a sequence of declarations that we summarize below.</html:p>
